title: All About Olivia Rodrigo
description:
This episode is all about Olivia Rodrigo, her rise to top and her relationship with Taylor Swift. Even though they became fast friends, Olivia still has a very cute reaction when she talks about Taylor! And honestly girl, same.
Olivia blew up this year but she's been around for a while. We break down Olivia's past, her relationship with Taylor, and this awesome debut album that she released!
How do you feel about Olivia's music? Let us know!
